{"id":148551,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/朝鲜战争研究专家徐泽荣获减刑/","date":"2011-04-29T08:30:31Z","modified":"2011-04-29T08:30:31Z","title":"朝鲜战争研究专家徐泽荣获减刑","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">据美联社报道，一个人权组织称，因研究中国在朝鲜战争所扮演角色而被判长期监禁的广东中山大学学者徐泽荣再获减刑，并有可能于今年</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月提前出狱。迄今，徐泽荣已在狱中度过</span><span>11</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年。总部在美国的对话基金会当地时间周四（</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>28</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）通报说，广州市中级法院决定给这名被控泄露国家机密的学者第三次减刑</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月。徐泽荣于</span><span>2000</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年被判处</span><span>13</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年徒刑，当时，中国安全部门正展开清除学界同境外有联系的</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">间谍网</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的行动。徐泽荣曾复印有关朝鲜战争的文件，用于研究。他认为，这些文件已经解密。中国军方则认定，这些文件当时依然属于保密级。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15038395%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E6%9C%9D%E9%B2%9C%E6%88%98%E4%BA%89%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E5%BE%90%E6%B3%BD%E8%8D%A3%E8%8E%B7%E5%87%8F%E5%88%91\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.f